  "feature": {
    "name": "Military Rank",
    "desc": [
      "You have a rank or position in a mercenary company, military order, or army. You retain your rank after leaving, and soldiers or mercenaries loyal to your organization recognize your authority. Tavernkeepers and inns provide food and lodging at reduced rates (simple lifestyle). You can requisition horses and carts for temporary use.",
